Enum SQLPart

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SQLPart>
      • org.efaps.db.wrapper.SQLPart
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SQLPart>

    public enum SQLPart
extends Enum<SQLPart>
    Enum is used to write the different standard sql part of a sql statement. This serves to elamintaed problems in future implementation of different databases.
